description: Pop-Gram is exploding onto the LA foodie scene, with their delectable selection of Kettle Corn creations, offering a range of flavors from pure comfort to healthy and light. Their 6-foot cart caters to all occasions from glamorous to casual, and can pop on site or simply provide creatively pre-packaged snacks. Pop-Gram is perfect for weddings, festivals, craft service, birthdays, and more! So make sure to have them pop on by and treat your guests to a positively scrumptious time.
name: Pop-Gram Kettle Corn
